Write a Python program to perform set operations on student activity groups.
The program should:

1. Accept names of students in three groups:

      Group A: Students who play Cricket

      Group B: Students who play Badminton

      Group C: Students who play Football


2. Display the following:

      List of students who play both Cricket and Badminton

      List of students who play either Cricket or Badminton but not Football

      Count of students who play neither Cricket nor Badminton

      Count of students who play both Cricket and Football but not Badminton
